com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.roads.nodematch
Class MatchNode

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.roads.nodematch.MatchNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class MatchNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Represents a matching of edges originating at two nodes. The matching is based only on the angles of the edges around each node.

Future

Allow angle to be computed from a length of the input linestring, not just the closest line segment (This will accomodate small ending line segments with angles which do not well represent the overall angle of the incident edge).
